headline: Cigna’s Evernorth to Scrap Drug Rebate Model for Upfront Discounts
summary: Cigna Group is launching a new rebate-free pharmacy benefit model which aims to bring down drug costs directly at the counter.

headline: Cigna’s Express Scripts to transition away from rebate drug model
summary: The massive PBM’s announcement comes as the drug middlemen attempt to lessen regulatory scrutiny. The company also said it will move to a cost-plus reimbursement model for in-network pharmacies.

headline: Evernorth Announces New Era of Pharmacy Benefit Services to Lower Americans' Medication Costs
summary: Evernorth, the health services division of The Cigna Group (NYSE:CI) today announced a new rebate-free pharmacy benefit model designed to help Americans stay healthy and get the medications they need by lowering costs, improving transparency, and supporting local pharmacies so care is always within reach.
